OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780063874
OL,3,CRob Elliot appointed as Carlisle
OL,4,CUnited Head Coach
OL,6,FCarlisle United have appointed Rob
OL,7,FElliot as their Head Coach following
OL,8,Fthe departure of Mark Hughes.
OL,10,FThe 40-year-old former Gateshead and
OL,11,FCrawley Town manager recently saved
OL,12,Fthe National League from relegation
OL,13,Fafter taking over at the club when
OL,14,Fthey were 11 points from safety.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780063874
OL,3,CRob Elliot appointed as Carlisle
OL,4,CUnited Head Coach
OL,6,FCarlisle United say that he has joined
OL,7,Fthe club on a rolling contract and
OL,8,Fthat "the club believes this is the
OL,9,Fright time to move forward with
OL,10,Fsomeone who can build on the progress
OL,11,Fmade last season, bring added drive
OL,12,Fand intensity, and develop a
OL,13,Ftactically flexible, front-foot,
OL,14,Fattacking team that plays with
OL,15,Fpurpose, creates chances and connects
OL,16,Fwith supporters."
OL,18,FSpeaking to Carlisle United, Rob
OL,19,FElliot said: "This is a huge club and
OL,20,Fopportunity, and I'm really excited to
OL,21,Fget started.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780063874
OL,3,CRob Elliot appointed as Carlisle
OL,4,CUnited Head Coach
OL,6,F"I want us to play attacking,
OL,7,Faggressive football with and without
OL,8,Fthe ball. We want to win, we want the
OL,9,Fplayers to enjoy it and want the fans
OL,10,Fto be excited to turn up and watch a
OL,11,Fteam that plays good football with an
OL,12,Fidentity but more importantly gives
OL,13,Fabsolutely everything for the badge.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780063874
OL,3,CRob Elliot appointed as Carlisle
OL,4,CUnited Head Coach
OL,6,F"We want to be adaptable. We want to
OL,7,Fget to know and understand the players
OL,8,Fwe have to get the best out of them on
OL,9,Fthe training ground and in games. We
OL,10,Fwant to have a clear plan when coming
OL,11,Fup against opposition. But we always
OL,12,Fwant to be positive, aggressive and
OL,13,Fbrave.
OL,15,F"I really like the owners' vision for
OL,16,Fthe club. Carlisle is a one club city
OL,17,Fand that matters. I know what it feels
OL,18,Flike when a football club is at the
OL,19,Fheart of a city, how important it is
OL,20,Fthat the team represent the fans,
OL,21,Fpeople and the community.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780063874
OL,3,CRob Elliot appointed as Carlisle
OL,4,CUnited Head Coach
OL,6,F"I know how much this means to the
OL,7,FPiatak family too. And they want the
OL,8,Fbest for not just the club but the
OL,9,Fcommunity as well.
OL,11,F"Everyone I have spoken to at the club
OL,12,Fhas been excellent with me. There is a
OL,13,Fstrong squad, there is young talent
OL,14,Fcoming through and there is a real
OL,15,Fopportunity to build something that
OL,16,Fpeople can feel part of.
OL,18,F"This is a brilliant football club,
OL,19,Fwith real ambition, and a fantastic
OL,20,Ffanbase ` I can't wait to get started."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780063874
OL,3,CRob Elliot appointed as Carlisle
OL,4,CUnited Head Coach
OL,6,FCarlisle United spent their first
OL,7,Fseason back in the National League
OL,8,Flast season but were eliminated in the
OL,9,Fplay-offs by Boreham Wood.
OL,11,FSpeaking to Carlisle United, Chairman
OL,12,FTom Piatak said: "Last season brought
OL,13,Fmore stability on the pitch, a third-
OL,14,Fplace finish and a squad that had
OL,15,Fstarted to move in the right direction.
OL,17,F"Rob's appointment is about building
OL,18,Fon that progress and taking the next
OL,19,Fstep. He has energy, drive and a clear
OL,20,Fsense of how he wants his teams to
OL,21,Fplay.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780063874
OL,3,CRob Elliot appointed as Carlisle
OL,4,CUnited Head Coach
OL,6,F"He has shown he can come into a
OL,7,Ffootball club, make an impact quickly,
OL,8,Fbuild belief and get players moving in
OL,9,Fthe right direction.
OL,11,F"We have a young, athletic and dynamic
OL,12,Fsquad, and we believe Rob's
OL,13,Fleadership, communication and coaching
OL,14,Fstyle will suit this group well.
OL,16,F"He understands the importance of
OL,17,Fwinning, but also the importance of
OL,18,Fbuilding something with purpose.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780063874
OL,3,CRob Elliot appointed as Carlisle
OL,4,CUnited Head Coach
OL,6,F"I would also like to thank everyone
OL,7,Fwho has contributed throughout this
OL,8,Fprocess. A number of people have given
OL,9,Ftheir time, insight and support, and I
OL,10,Fwould especially like to thank Paul
OL,11,FHart for his guidance and experience.
OL,12,FHis input has been valuable as we have
OL,13,Fworked through this decision carefully
OL,14,Fand professionally.
OL,16,F"We are excited to welcome Rob to
OL,17,FCarlisle United and look forward to
OL,18,Fworking with him."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOUzD@RO]
